== 制作 ==
[[File:A_Cure_for_Pokeritis.ogv|thumb]]
《治疗扑克上瘾》是维塔格拉夫制片厂制作的多部单卷或更短的喜剧[[短片|短片]]之一，这些短片均为家庭喜剧题材，由邦尼和芬奇主演，人称“邦尼格拉夫”（{{lang|en|Bunnygraphs}}）或“邦尼芬奇”（{{lang|en|Bunnyfinches}}）<ref name="LoC">{{cite press release | title = 2011 National Film Registry More Than a Box of Chocolates | series = News from the Library of Congress | publisher = Library of Congress | accessdate = 2014-08-29 | date = 2011-12-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140704135038/http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2011/11-240.html | issn = 0731-3527 | url = http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2011/11-240.html | archivedate = 2014-07-04}}</ref><ref name="McCaffrey-Jacobs-1999">{{cite book | author = McCaffrey D, Jacobs CP. | title = Guide to the Silent Years of American Cinema | series = Reference Guides to the World's Cinema | year = 1999 | publisher = Greenwood | isbn = 978-0-313-30345-6}}</ref>{{rp|121}}。由于维塔格拉夫制片厂的影片普遍没有存档，所以这些短片起初制作的确切数量仍不得而知<ref name="Brewster-2005">{{cite book | author = Brewster B. | editor = Abel R. | title = Encyclopedia of Early Cinema | chapter = Vitagraph Company of America | year = 2005 | publisher = Routledge | isbn = 978-0-415-23440-5 | pages = 679–681}}</ref>。不同来源中估计的数据也有很大不同，有超过150部的<ref name="Slide-Grevison-1987">{{cite book | author = Slide A, Grevison A. | title = The Big V: A History of the Vitagraph Company | year = 1987 | publisher = Scarecrow Press | isbn = 978-0-8108-2030-2 | page = 47}}</ref>，有超过200部的<ref name="Brewster-2005" />，还有超过260部的<ref name="Lowe-2004">{{cite book | author = Lowe D. | title = An Encyclopedic Dictionary of Women in Early American Films: 1895–1930 | year = 2004 | publisher = Routledge | isbn = 978-0-7890-1843-4 | page = 208}}</ref>，其中大部分如今都已佚失<ref name="Cullen-2006">{{cite book | author = Cullen F. | title = Vaudeville, Old and New: An Encyclopedia of Variety Performers in America | year = 2006 | publisher = Routledge | isbn = 978-0-415-93853-2 | page = 157}}</ref>。

这部影片也是早期电影试图突破常规画面运动和定位的一个范例。片中“警察”突袭的一场戏无论镜头前还是镜头后都同时有动作进行，演员可以在其间穿行，以此表现出镜头的纵深程度。这一[[电影摄影|拍摄]]技巧提高了镜头的真实性和影片的节奏感。<ref name="Keil-2002">{{cite book | author = Keil C. | title = Early American Cinema in Transition: Story, Style, and Filmmaking, 1907–1913 | series = Wisconsin Studies in Film | year = 2002 | publisher = University of Wisconsin Press | isbn = 978-0-299-17364-7 | pages = 133–134}}</ref><ref name="McCaffrey-1968">{{cite book | author = McCaffrey D. | title = 4 Great Comedians: Chaplin, Lloyd, Keaton, Langdon | year = 1968 | series = International Film Guide Series | publisher = Zwemmer | oclc = 309961 | page = 16}}</ref>

== 音乐 ==
剧院在放映[[无声电影|无声电影]]时会附有各种类型的音乐伴奏，根据电影及播放场地的不同，伴奏的音乐有可能是现场[[钢琴|钢琴]]或[[管弦乐|管弦乐]]团演奏，也可能是预先录制的曲目，或者完全没有音乐<ref name="Altman-2007">{{cite book | author = Altman R. | title = Silent Film Sound | series = Film and Culture | year = 2007 | publisher = Columbia University Press | isbn = 978-0-231-11663-3}}</ref>{{rp|199-200}}。一些影片中会带有提示文字表明音乐的播放时间，或是选择一些特定的歌曲作为伴奏<ref name=Marks-1997>{{cite book | author = Marks MM. | title = Music and the Silent Film: Contexts and Case Studies, 1895–1924 | url = https://archive.org/details/musicsilentfilmc00mark | year = 1997 | publisher = Oxford University Press | isbn = 978-0-19-506891-7 | page = [https://archive.org/details/musicsilentfilmc00mark/page/68 68]}}</ref>。1910至1912年间，选定的歌曲以[[流行音乐|流行音乐]]为主<ref name="Altman-2007" />{{rp|223}}，这主要是因为这些歌曲的歌名或歌词与电影间存在某方面联系，或是为了与影片形成对比而提供带有恰当[[织体_(音乐)|织体]]的音乐<ref name="Altman-2001">{{cite book | author = Altman R. | editor = Wojcik PR, Knight A. | title = Soundtrack Available: Essays on Film and Popular Music | chapter = Cinema and Popular Song: The Lost Tradition | year = 2001 | publisher = Duke University Press | isbn = 978-0-8223-2800-1 | page = 22}}</ref>。从1910年开始，维塔格拉夫为其制作的所有影片都提供了伴奏曲目名单<ref name="Altman-2007" />{{rp|256}}。

维塔格拉夫为《治疗扑克上瘾》推荐的音乐中首先是《我很高兴我结婚了》{{#tag:ref|原名为“{{lang|en|I'm Glad I'm Married}}”，[[阿尔伯特·冯·提尔泽|阿尔伯特·冯·提尔泽]]（{{lang|en|Albert Von Tilzer}}）作曲，[[杰克·诺沃斯|杰克·诺沃斯]]（{{lang|en|Jack Norworth}}）作词<ref name="Copyright890">{{cite journal | journal = Catalogue of Copyright Entries Part 3: Musical Compositions | series = new series | volume = 3 | issue = 40–44 | date = 1908-10 | page = 890}}</ref>。|group="注"}}和《我盯上你了》{{#tag:ref|原名为“{{lang|en|I've Got My Eyes on You}}”，西奥多·莫尔斯（{{lang|en|Theodore F. Morse}}）作曲，{{lang|en|F·W}}·海格（{{lang|en|F. W. Hager}}）和{{lang|en|J}}·林格本（{{lang|en|J. Ringelben}}）作词<ref name="UTSheet">{{cite web | title = I've Got My Eyes on You | work = The UT Sheet Music Collection | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140529051419/http://diglib.lib.utk.edu/utsmc/main.php?bid=1977 | publisher = University of Tennessee | url = http://diglib.lib.utk.edu/utsmc/main.php?bid=1977 | accessdate = 2014-08-29 | archivedate = 2014-05-29 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。接下来又推荐在乔治向夫人宣称自己要去参加兄弟会活动时播放《我不相信你》{{#tag:ref|原名为“{{lang|en|I Don't Believe You}}”，[[哈利·冯·提尔泽|哈利·冯·提尔泽]]（{{lang|en|Harry Von Tilzer}}）作曲，威廉·狄龙（{{lang|en|William Dillon}}）作词<ref name="Copyright">{{cite journal | journal = Catalogue of Copyright Entries Part 3: Musical Compositions | series = new series | volume = 5 | issue = 44–47 |date= 1910-11}}</ref>{{rp|1344}}。|group="注"}}或《我是帕齐俱乐部的荣誉会员》{{#tag:ref|原名为“{{lang|en|I'm an Honorary Member of the Patsy Club}}”，哈利·冯·提尔泽作曲，安德鲁·斯特林（{{lang|en|Andrew B. Sterling}}）作词<ref name="Copyright" />{{rp|1345}}。|group="注"}}。男主角说梦话时的伴奏曲目则是《如果你说梦话，别提我的名字》{{#tag:ref|原名为“{{lang|en|If You Talk in Your Sleep, Don't Mention My Name}}”，[[纳特·艾耶尔|纳特·艾耶尔]]（{{lang|en|Nat Ayer}}）作曲，西摩·布朗（{{lang|en|A. Seymour Brown}}）作词，[[杰罗姆·H·雷米克|杰罗姆·H·雷米克]]（{{lang|en|Jerome H. Remick}}）发行<ref name="Jasen-2002">{{cite book | editor = Jasen DA. | title = A Century of American Popular Music: 2000 Best-Loved and Remembered Songs (1899–1999) | url = https://archive.org/details/centuryofamerica0000jase | publisher = Routledge | year = 2002 | isbn = 978-0-415-93700-9 | page = [https://archive.org/details/centuryofamerica0000jase/page/93 93]}}</ref>。|group="注"}}，接下来则是弗雷迪进行调查时播放的《回工厂去，玛丽》{{#tag:ref|原名为“{{lang|en|Back to the Factory, Mary}}”，词曲均由克拉伦斯·加斯基尔（{{lang|en|Clarence Gaskill}}）创作<ref name="Copyright1616">{{cite journal | journal = Catalogue of Copyright Entries Part 3: Musical Compositions | series = new series | volume = 6 | issue = 13 | year = 1911 | page = 1616}}</ref>。|group="注"}}，以及“警察”突袭时播放的《啊哦我亲爱的》{{#tag:ref|原名为“{{lang|en|Whoops, My Dear}}”，伯特·格兰特（{{lang|en|Bert F. Grant}}）作曲，比利·莫里西（{{lang|en|Billy J. Morrissey}}）作词，杰罗姆·{{lang|en|H}}·雷米克发行<ref name="Copyright" />{{rp|1422}}。|group="注"}}，最终电影结束时播放的曲目则是《别带我回家》{{#tag:ref|原名为“{{lang|en|Don't Take Me Home}}”，哈利·冯·提尔泽作曲，文森特·布莱恩（{{lang|en|Vincent P. Bryan}}）作词<ref name="DTMH">{{cite web | title = Don't Take Me Home | website = National Jukebox | publisher = Library of Congress | url = http://www.loc.gov/jukebox/recordings/detail/id/1465 | accessdate = 2014-08-29 | archivedate = 2014-07-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140713222707/http://www.loc.gov/jukebox/recordings/detail/id/1465/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="VLP14">{{cite journal | title = Music Suggestions | journal = Vitagraph Life Portrayals | volume = 1 | issue = 16 | date = 1912-02-17 | page = 14}}</ref>。

== 评价和影响 ==
从类型片的角度看，“邦尼格拉夫”是这一时期电影的代表作品<ref name="Brewster-2005" />，这些作品非常成功，约翰·邦尼成为第一位美国喜剧电影明星，弗洛拉·芬奇也成为第一位女笑星<ref name="LoC" /><ref name="Cullen-2006" />。《治疗扑克上瘾》于1912年2月23日发行<ref name="VLP13" />，获得了良好的评价，还有在美国以外的美国放映。[[新西兰|新西兰]]的《泰晤士星报》（{{lang|en|''Thames Star''}}）形容影片“好笑得令人讶异”<ref name="Thames">{{cite news | title = Local and General | work = Thames Star | location = Thames, New Zealand | date = 1912-09-14 | page = 2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140616204947/http://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/cgi-bin/paperspast?a=d&d=THS19120914.1.2&e=-------10--1----0-- | url = http://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/cgi-bin/paperspast?a=d&d=THS19120914.1.2&e=-------10--1----0-- | archivedate = 2014-06-16 | accessdate = 2014-08-29}}</ref>。约翰·邦尼去世后，他的作品仍然很受欢迎，维塔格拉夫为此于1917年宣布会重新发行包括本片（更名为《扑克治疗良方》）在内的多部由他出演的电影，作为“最受欢迎电影精选”推出<ref name="Moto">{{cite journal | title = John Bunny is Back! | journal = Motography | date = 1917-06-23 | volume = 17 | issue = 25 | page = 1331 | url = http://www.archive.org/stream/motography17elec#page/1330/mode/2up | accessdate = 2014-08-29}}</ref>。不过，《治疗扑克上瘾》的喜剧风格随着时间的推移变得过时，特别是在面对[[马克·森内特|马克·森内特]]（{{lang|en|Mack Sennett}}）的闹剧影片以及之后[[查理·卓别林|查理·卓别林]]和[[巴斯特·基顿|巴斯特·基顿]]等喜剧演员的作品时对比尤其明显<ref name="McCaffrey-Jacobs-1999" />{{rp|59}}<ref name="Nuckols">{{cite news | author = Nuckols B. | title = 'Forrest Gump' to be preserved in US film registry | agency = Associated Press | date = 2011-12-27 | newspaper = San Diego Union-Tribune | url = http://www.utsandiego.com/news/2011/dec/27/forrest-gump-to-be-preserved-in-us-film-registry/ | accessdate = 2014-08-29}}</ref>。据电影学者唐纳德·麦卡弗里（{{lang|en|Donald McCaffrey}}）和克里斯托弗·雅各布斯（{{lang|en|Christopher Jacobs}}）表示，虽然其中演员功力值得称道，但现代观众在观看本片的过程中恐怕“很难闪烁出一丝的微笑”<ref name="McCaffrey-Jacobs-1999" />{{rp|59}}。

[[File:Sitting_up_with_a_Sick_Friend.jpg|thumb]]的狗]]
电影的主题及其与之后诞生艺术作品之间的关系一直是批判性分析的话题。《治疗扑克上瘾》可能是第一部描绘扑克牌局的电影，其中反映出当时大众对这种赌局的看法：一种以男性为主导的社会疾病。[[卡修斯·马塞勒斯·库利奇|卡修斯·马塞勒斯·柯立芝]]1903年推出的的《狗玩扑克牌》（{{lang|en|''Dogs Playing Poker''}}）系列画作中也表现出类似的看法，其中一幅《与病友同坐》（{{lang|en|''Sitting up with a Sick Friend''}}）与本片情节很相似<ref name="CNN">{{cite web | title = 'Dogs Playing Poker' sell for $590K | website = CNNMoney | date = 2005-02-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413150049/http://money.cnn.com/2005/02/16/news/newsmakers/poker_dogs/ | deadurl = no | url = http://money.cnn.com/2005/02/16/news/newsmakers/poker_dogs/ | accessdate = 2014-08-29 | archivedate = 2014-04-13}}</ref><ref name="Harris">{{cite web | author = Harris M. | title = Pop Poker: Poker and Pop-Culture Stigma in the Early 1900s | website = PokerListings | date = 2013-02-05 | accessdate = 2014-08-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130208071626/http://www.pokerlistings.com/pop-poker-poker-and-pop-culture-stigma-in-the-early-1900s-90954 | url = http://www.pokerlistings.com/pop-poker-poker-and-pop-culture-stigma-in-the-early-1900s-90954 | archivedate = 2013-02-08}}</ref>。有评论中将《治疗扑克上瘾》与20世纪末以及40年代的[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]相比较<ref name="McCaffrey-Jacobs-1999" />{{rp|121}}<ref name="King-2002">{{cite book | author = King G. | title = Film Comedy | year = 2002 | publisher = Wallflower Press | isbn = 978-1-903364-35-2}}</ref>{{rp|23}}。[[鲍尔州立大学|鲍尔州立大学]]的电影[[历史学家|历史学家]]韦斯·格林（{{lang|en|Wes Gehring}}）认为，乔治是现代[[反英雄|反英雄]]原型的先驱，并将布朗夫妇和[[劳莱与哈台|劳莱与哈台]]相提并论<ref name="Gehring-2004">{{cite book | author = Gehring WD. | title = Leo McCarey: From Marx to McCarthy | url = https://archive.org/details/leomccareyfromma0000gehr | series = The Scarecrow Filmmakers | year = 2004 | publisher = Scarecrow Press | isbn = 978-0-8108-5263-1 | page = [https://archive.org/details/leomccareyfromma0000gehr/page/62 62]}}</ref>。还有作家研究了电影中的性别问题。[[杰拉尔德·麦斯特|杰拉尔德·麦斯特]]（{{lang|en|Gerald Mast}}）认为，电影的喜剧基础是男子气概和[[女性主义|女性主义]][[道德|道德]]观之间的冲突<ref name="Mast-1979">{{cite book | author = Mast G. | title = The Comic Mind: Comedy and the Movies | year = 1979 | publisher = University of Chicago Press | edition = 2nd | isbn = 978-0-226-50978-5 | page = 41}}</ref>。[[布鲁内尔大学|布鲁内尔大学]]讲师杰夫·金（{{lang|en|Geoff King}}）认为，男主角对逃离妻子“囚禁”的努力尝试是无声喜剧片中经常出现的主题<ref name="King-2002" />{{rp|130}}，影评人彼得·纳什（{{lang|en|Peter Nash}}）认为，“挑剔而女性化”的弗雷迪是现代男同性恋角色的代表<ref name="Nash">{{cite web | author = Nash P. | title = A Cure for Pokeritis | website = Three Movie Buffs | date = 2010-10-18 | url = http://www.threemoviebuffs.com/review/cure-for-pokeritis | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140408220316/http://www.threemoviebuffs.com/review/cure-for-pokeritis | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-29 | archivedate = 2014-04-08}}</ref>。

2011年，本片因其在“文化、历史和审美方面的显著成就”，由[[国会图书馆_(美国)|美国国会图书馆]]作为邦尼芬奇电影的代表作品列入[[国家电影登记部|国家电影登记部]]下属的[[国家电影登记表|国家电影登记表]]保护电影名单<ref name="LoC" />。

== 家用媒体 ==
